abstract: With few colleagues of color in the four big agencies, these representatives have an impact on what is produced. But they also face isolation and other barriers.
snippet: With few colleagues of color in the four big agencies, these representatives have an impact on what is produced. But they also face isolation and other barriers.
lead_paragraph: Movies like “Black Panther” and “Crazy Rich Asians” don’t come around all that often partly because of how projects are put together. Chances are the people brokering those deals — and determining who gets in the door and what stories are told — are white.

snippet: Since you provide the content for this group’s delightful hip-hop musical improvisation, you really have to lend them your ears (and phones).
lead_paragraph: Upon arrival at the Greenwich House Theater to see “Freestyle Love Supreme,” the mostly improvised and entirely delightful hip-hop musical that opened there on Tuesday, you will be asked to turn off your phone and lock it in a Yondr pouch. There it will remain until an usher liberates it when the show is over, 75 minutes later.

abstract: With the social media company unresponsive, a police veteran in Germany is using shoe-leather detective work to combat online misinformation and hate.

lead_paragraph: TRAUNSTEIN, Germany — The rumor began, as so many do these days, on Facebook.

abstract: Bears on the Novaya Zemlya island chain halted a seasonal migration to congregate near a military outpost, in a possible omen of climate change.
snippet: Bears on the Novaya Zemlya island chain halted a seasonal migration to congregate near a military outpost, in a possible omen of climate change.
lead_paragraph: MOSCOW — Dozens of polar bears have laid siege to a small military settlement deep in the Russian Arctic, leaving residents afraid to send their children to school, or even open their front doors.
